---
title: Speedy Pesto, Bacon & Courgette Farfalle with Garlic Pangrattato & Pine Nuts
description: This fresh, green farfalle is the perfect combination of tasty and light. Add a bit of gusto with crispy bacon and a crunchy garlic pangrattato on top and it'll leave you feeling satisfied on every level.
